<i>noun</i>: 혜택 [혜ː택/헤ː택], 편익 [펴닉], 이점 [이ː쩜], 유익 [유ː익] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>혜택 [혜ː택/헤ː택]</dt><br>
<dd>benefit; advantage</dd><br>
<dd>제도나 환경, 다른 사람 등으로부터 받는 도움이나 이익.</dd><br>
<dd>Help or benefit from an institution or environment, or another person.</dd><br>
<dt>편익 [펴닉]</dt><br>
<dd>convenience; advantage</dd><br>
<dd>편리하고 유익함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of something being handy and beneficial.</dd><br>
<dt>이점 [이ː쩜]</dt><br>
<dd>advantage; merit</dd><br>
<dd>이익이 되는 점.</dd><br>
<dd>A thing beneficial to someone.</dd><br>
<dt>유익 [유ː익]</dt><br>
<dd>advantage</dd><br>
<dd>이롭거나 도움이 될 만함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of something being beneficial or helpful.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>